Description.Text:
Discover South Seas Island Resort- a serene village and wildlife sanctuary unto itself - marked by white-sand beaches, coastal waters that glisten with a million shades of blue, and endless opportunity. Encompassing 330 acres along two-and-half miles of powder-white beaches lapped by turquoise tides, step into a world of comfortable, serene, and exceptional accommodations surrounded by the wonders of nature. Discover the extensive playground right outside the door from your stunning Captiva Island lodging. Engage in a challenging match on the tennis court. Charter a boat for some breathtaking back bay fishing. Relax under the tropical sun poolside. Take the entire family on an sea kayaking nature tour. Travel on the trolley that traverses through town and watch the sunset over the bay. Simply delight in this idyllic setting.
Facility Includes : - Complimentary parking - Complimentary Wireless Internet - In-room safe - Dataport - Daily newspaper delivery - Coffeemaker - Refrigerator - Flat screen TV - VCR or DVD player - Desk - Access to washer and dryer - 19 day and night tennis courts - Championship nine-hole golf - 11 pools and 2 hot tubs - Sea kayaks and sailboats - Jet skis and parasailing - Harbourside Bar & Grill - Sunset Beach Chalet - Business center - Fitness center

- No trip or quad occupancy available in the One Bedroom Beach Villa. - Rates are inclusive of resort fee. - Unless notified prior to, or at check-in, a one night penalty will apply to departures that occur earlier than the date specified on the original reservation.
